2017-10-26  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	This ChangeLog file is discontinued. Please use git log instead.

2017-10-25  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/app.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/ovaldefs/details.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/ovaldefs/detailspage.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/ovaldefs/row.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/ovaldefs/table.js: Implement oval definition
	details page.

