	* src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/capabilities/capabilities.js: Use info for
	checking ovaldef capabilities.

2017-10-25  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/models/ovaldef.js: Improve parsing of ovaldef
	data for displaying the details.

