2017-10-25  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/entity/container.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/cpes/detailspage.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/cves/detailspage.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/nvts/detailspage.js: The permission
	component isn't passed to EntityContainer anymore. Therefore change property
	to deactivate loading of permissions.

2017-10-25  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/components/notification/dialognotification.js:
	DialogNotification uses the render props pattern. Therefore require children
	to be a function.

2017-10-25  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/components/dialog/dialog.js: Remove the width
	and visibility states from the new dialog component. They must be handled in
	the parent component already and shouldn't be duplicated in the dialog.

