	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/entity/withEntityContainer.js: Pass only
	necessary props to EntityContainer. All other props go to its child.

2017-10-12  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/entity/container.js: Be more explicit about
	what's going to be passed to child components from an EntityContainer.

2017-10-12  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/entity/permissions.js: Call onChange handler if
	a entity permission has been created.

2017-10-12  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/entity/withComponent.js: Don't forget to pass
	action handler to child componets and to add handlers for cloning.

2017-10-12  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/permissions/listpage.js: Implement
	permissions page with PermissionComponent instead of withPermissionsComponent
	HOC. With this change it is easier to understand what's happening when
	building the permissions page. Also the EntityPage customization can happen
	directly by passing the corresponding props to the EntityPage component
	instead of passing them through the withEntitiesContainer HOC.

2017-10-12  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/entity/container.js: Export composed component
	directly. No need to store it in a variable before.

2017-10-12  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/permissions/withPermissionsComponent.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/targets/withTargetComponent.js: Use
	withComponent function to implement withTargetComponent and
	withPermissionsComponent HOCs. Implementing both is now an one liner.

2017-10-12  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/permissions/component.js: Extract a
	PermissionComponent from withPermissionsComponent HOC. The new component uses
	the render props pattern.

2017-10-12  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/entity/withComponent.js: Add a withComponent
	function to create withXyzComponent HOCs easily. When using the render props
	pattern for entity components all withXyzComponent HOCs are build the same.

2017-10-12  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/entity/container.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/entity/withEntityContainer.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/cves/detailspage.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/hosts/detailspage.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/notes/detailspage.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/nvts/detailspage.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/os/detailspage.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/overrides/detailspage.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/results/detailspage.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/targets/detailspage.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/tasks/detailspage.js: Extract
	withEntityContainer HOC into an own js module.

2017-10-12  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/entity/container.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/entity/tagshandler.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/entity/withHandleTags.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/reports/summary.js: Convert withHandleTags
	HOC into a TagsHandler component. The new TagsHandler component uses the
	render props pattern and should be easier to understand then the HOC.

2017-10-11  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/entity/permissions.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/hosts/detailspage.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/pages/hosts/withHostComponent.js,
