2017-10-06  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/http.js: Don't pass undefined values as url
	parameter. Most of the time using a undefined value as a url parameter is a
	bug. If it may be indented it must be passed as a string now. Also use ES6
	syntax for iterating of the params.

