2017-09-28  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/http.js: Add support for CancelToken in all http
	requests. Canceling a request will result in a promise rejection with
	REASON_CANCEL set. This can be checked in the promise.catch method then.

