	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/components/powerfilter/powerfilter.js: Use
	glamorous for styling the powerfilter and get rid of the css file. Improve
	layout of powerfilter if the filter term gets longer. Don't align powerfilter
	on the left by default. Only align its content. Let parent components align
	the powerfilter.

2017-08-29  Michael Wiegand <michael.wiegand@greenbone.net>

	Make it possible skip dependency checks during configuration. This
	makes it possible to generate documentation and source tarballs in
	environments where said dependencies are not present.

	* CMakeLists.txt: Move dependency checks to 'src/' directory. Do not
	consider this subdirectory containing code and dependency checks when
	SKIP_SRC is defined.

	* src/CMakeLists.txt: Explicitly check for all dependencies since this
	is no longer done by the top-level CMakeLists.txt.

