	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/components/form/withChangeHandler.js: Allow
	using a string for setting the debounce timeout value. Also fix change handler
	for the uncontrolled input when no value prop is set by the parent component.

2017-08-18  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/utils.js: Change parse_float to behave like
	parse_int. If both value conversions got not a number (NaN) the parsing
	functions return undefined now.

2017-08-18  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/components/form/withChangeHandler.js: Allow to
	debounce all change handlers. debouncing lowers the interval when change
	handlers are called. This is often required for scoll handlers or filter
	inputs to reduce the amount of re-rendering cycles.

