	a composable HOC.

2017-08-03  Michael Wiegand <michael.wiegand@greenbone.net>

	* CMakeLists.txt: Remove -O2 from being added to
	CMAKE_C_FLAGS_RELEASE. This actually causes optimization flags from
	CMAKE_C_FLAGS_RELEASE to be duplicated or even superseded for no good
	reason.

2017-08-03  Jan-Oliver Wagner <jan-oliver.wagner@greenbone.net>

	* CMakeLists.txt: Move location of certificates from
	lib/openvas/ to lib/gvm/. This requires to copy over
	the already installed certficates which should happen
	as part of updating a today's version of module "gvm".

