2017-06-29  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/index.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/app.js: Add an index.js file for src/gmp. This
	allows import Gmp from 'gmp' now.

