2017-06-29  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/package.json: Set NODE_PATH to src directory. This
	allows to import our packges without relative paths. E.g. now it is possible
	to "import Model from 'gmp/model.js';" instead of having to use and adjust
	relative paths.

