2017-06-19  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/divider/divider.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/divider/icondivider.js: Introduce new divider
	components. This components can be used to add a margin between its children.
	This replaces the box property of layout components and should be used
	instead. Using a divider is much more flexible because the size of the margin
	can be set dynamically.

