	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/table/simple.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/table/stripped.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/table/table.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/yarn.lock: Use glamorous
	(https://github.com/paypal/glamorous) instead of styled-components. It has a
	comparable api but uses object syntax instead of template literals. IMHO it is
	much easier to understand and also it doesn't need an extra runtime css
	parser.

