	* INSTALL, src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt: create react app 1.0 and its
	dependencies are requiring node 6 now. This isn't optimal because even in
	debian testing and ubuntu only version 4 is packaged. Nevertheless node 6 is
	the proposed active lts version
	(see https://github.com/nodejs/LTS#lts-schedule1).

