2017-04-11 Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/proptypes.js: In react 15.5 using
	React.PropTypes creates a warning. With react 16.0 PropTypes will be removed
	from the React namespace. Therefore prepare to use our own object for all
	PropTypes in future.

