2017-03-02  Timo Pollmeier <timo.pollmeier@greenbone.net>

	Allow to override default image URLs, for example to allow report
	formats to use images embedded in the HTML/JavaScript.

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/icons/icon.js: Use new get_img_url
	function to get src URL of img element.

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/img.js: Use new get_img_url function
	to get src URL of img element.

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/urls.js: New file.  Manages URL
	overrides.

2017-03-02  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/targets/dialogcontainer.js: Rename
	handleCreateTarget method to handleSaveTarget. It already did saving changes
	and creating a new target.

