2017-03-01  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/notes/dialog.js: Remove debug output.

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/notes/row.js: Fix link to note details and title
	of export button.

2017-02-28  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad.c (main): Increase session timeout limit from 1 day two 4 weeks.
	Also display default timeout in console help.

2017-02-28  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_http.c: Fix cookie handling for newer browsers if server time is
	behind the client. RFC 6265 defines a max-age parameter for Set-Cookie header
	that defines a cookie lifetime in seconds from now (see
	https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc6265#section-4.1.2.2 for more details). Newer
	browsers (> IE 8) already understand max-age. max-age takes precedence before
	expire. Therefore we can keep the possibly outdated expire for older browsers.

2017-02-28  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_http.c: Use RFC 2616
	(https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2616#section-3.3.1) compliant date format for
	Set-Cookie http header expire param.

2017-02-28  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

