2017-02-22  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/gmp.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/http.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/app.js: Improve HttpInterceptor handling by
	using promises. Interceptors can now transform errors into valid responses
	and/or absorb specific errors. E.g. now the 401 responses won't be bubbling
	as an error through the whole stack and therefore don't show up in the
	browsers console anymore.

