	prop types are used in development mode to validate the properties passed to
	components.

2017-01-30 Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt: Fix building bundle if js source files
	have changed. Setting a cmake variable on the PARENT_SCOPE doesn't set the
	variable on the current scope. As a result the js source files haven't been
	used as dependencies for running build in the ng directory.

