2017-01-25 Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/gmp.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/app.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/header.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/login.js: Move handling of window.gsa and it's
