2017-01-25 Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/cache.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/command.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/commands/users.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/gmp.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/http.js: Implement a simple http caching. The
	caching is only possible for http get requests and must be set explicitly.
	Currently it is only used for the settings. The downside of the caching is
	that saving the dashboard layout will not be reflected in the settings without
	a full reload. The cache class itself should be improved to be a lru cache
	with a maximum of entries in future to save memory. The cache will be cleared
	if the user is logged in.

2017-01-25 Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/results/results.js: Remove text from solution
	type column and reduce the size of the column.

