2017-01-23 Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_omp.c (get_many): Allow to pass details parameter to omp many
	requests. For reports the details parameter is always 0. I don't see any
	reason for this but this is the original behaviour.

2017-01-23 Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/gmp.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/http.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/gmp/promise.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/utils.js: Move PromiseFactory from utils to an own
	module. Improve Http class to support timeouts and prepare it for cancelling
	request promises. Cancelling isn't possible at the moment. It would require to
	use a promise libary because cancelling promises has been withdrawn from
	ecma script standardization. E.g. bluebird library would support cancelling.

2017-01-23 Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt: Add list of css files for ng. Building
	ng depends on the css files because changes on theses files must cause a
	rebuild of the bundles. Whitout rebuilding the css changes wouldn't be
	included in the production bundles.

2017-01-23  Jan-Oliver Wagner <jan-oliver.wagner@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad.c: Include gvm/base/logging.h instead of
	openvas/misc/openvas_logging.h.

2017-01-22  Jan-Oliver Wagner <jan-oliver.wagner@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad.c (main): Enable GNUTLS bugging if the
	respective environment variable is set. This code
	was moved from the function setup_log_handlers() to
	this place in order to not make gnutls a mandatory
	requirement for the general logging module.

