	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/tasks/tasks.js,
	src/html/classic/ng/src/web/tasks/taskslist.js:
	Simplify list pages by removing a complete component hierarchy. All states are
	moved into the top page component. For new list pages only two components have
	to be developed instead of three now. This reduces the code complexity for
	list pages a lot.

