2016-12-20  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad.c, src/gsad_cmd.c, src/gsad_content_type.h, src/gsad_http.c:
	Remove content type GSAD_CONTENT_TYPE_APPLICATION_HTML. There is no
	application/html MIME type defined. Either it is text/html or
	application/xhtml+xml. Also they default content type should for formats
	should be application/octet-stream which means unkown binary data and not
	html.

