	Remove now obsolete properties of gsad_connection_info struct. A connection
	info should not contain response related data.

2016-12-19  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad.c, src/gsad_http.h, src/gsad_http_handler.c: Refactor exec_omp_post
	and exec_omp_post to use more common code and behave more the same. Both
	functions return either MHD_NO or MHD_YES now and are creating the responses
	internally. There is still some room for optimizing exec_omp_get by using http
	handlers for the credential and user handling as like the get part.

