2016-12-15  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	Unify response data handling

	* src/gsad.c, src/gsad_http.c, src/gsad_http.h, src/gsad_http_handler.c,
	src/gsad_omp.c, src/gsad_omp.h: Always use cmd_response_data_t to return
	content type, content length, status code and content disposition from omp
	functions. This allows to use the same function signature for most omp
	functions.

2016-12-15  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_cmd.h, src/gsad_cmd.c: Add content_length and content_disposition
	to cmd_response_data_t. Also add getter and setter functions. This will allow
	to use cmd_response_data_t really for all response data in the omp functions.

2016-12-15  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_omp.c (xsl_transform_omp): Set content type to xml if xml flag is
	set and xml content will be returned in xsl_transform_omp.

2016-12-15  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_http_handler.c (handle_omp_get): Let command function set the
	returned content type.

2016-12-15  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_http_handler.c (handle_omp_get): Don't use params from credentials.
	Always use them from connection info struct.

2016-12-15  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_cmd.h, src/gsad_cmd.c: Add getters and setters for
	cmd_response_data_t content type and status code.

2016-12-15  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt: Use YARN_FOUND instead of Yarn_FOUND.
	CMake from debian stable seems not recognizing the lower case variable.

2016-12-14  Jan-Oliver Wagner <jan-oliver.wagner@greenbone.net>

	* README: Updated text and removed the detailed output of --help which
	it too easily outdated here.

	* src/gsad.c: Add all licenses to the Doxygen documentation.

	* COPYING: Fix filename.

2016-12-14  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_omp.c, src/gsad_omp.h: Remove manager_connect from all omp command
	functions. Instead pass a openvas_connection_t pointer to all these functions.
	This allows to create a connection and handle the connection failure on less
	places and avoids to closing and opening several connections when executing
	many omp commands in sequence.

	* src/gsad.c, src/gsad_http_handler.c: Create connection to manager before
	executing omp command functions.

2016-12-14  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad.c, src/gsad_http.c, src/gsad_http_handler.c: Use new
	gsad_message_new function instead of gsad_message.

2016-12-14  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_http.h, src/gsad.c (exec_omp_get): Expect gsad_connection_info as
	parameter instead of http connection. Use already parsed params from passed
	connnection info.

	* src/gsad_http_handler.c (handle_omp_get): Pass con_info instead of http
	connection to exec_omp_get.

2016-12-14  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_http_handler.c (handle_request): Add params to con_info also for
	get requests. In future the params of con_info should be used always instead
	of the params from the credentials in get requests.

2016-12-14  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_http.c, src/gsad_http.h: Introduce new logout_xml function. This
	function encapsulates the generation of the logout page.

2016-12-14  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_http.c, src/gsad_http.h: Extract a gsad_message_new function from
	gsad_message. This function has a new xml_flag parameter to allow to decide
	to return xml or html explicitly. In future the gsad_message function shold be
	replaces by gsad_message_new completely.

2016-12-14  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_user.c, src/gsad_user.h: Introduce new logout function.

2016-12-14  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_base.c, src/gsad_params.h: Add new function params_value_bool.

