2016-12-13  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_http.c, src/gsad_http_handler.c, src/gsad_omp.c: Set ng element on
	envelope xml if USE_GSA_NG is defined.

	* src/html/classic/gsad.xsl: Link global dashboard and tasks in menu to gsa ng
	if envelope contains ng element.

2016-12-13  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/js/greenbone.js: Add function to set the current token. The
	token is also stored in the session storage which allows for better
	interoperability with gsa ng without having to relogin.

	* src/html/classic/graphics.xsl: Remove setting the js gsa token from
	graphics.xsl. Setting the token is now included in gsad.xsl.

	* src/html/classic/gsad.xsl: Use new gsa.set_token function to always store
	the current token in the session storage.

2016-12-13  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* cmake/FindPythonModule.cmake, src/po/CMakeLists.txt: Move
	FindPythonModule.cmake from root to cmake directory.

2016-12-13  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	Allow to activate gsa ng single page app

	* CMakeLists.txt: Load cmake modules from cmake/ subdir and allow to activate
	gsa ng with the USE_GSA_NG cmake switch (-DCMAKE_GSA_NG=yes)

	* cmake/FindNode.cmake, cmake/FindNpm.cmake, cmake/FindYarn.cmake: Add find
	package cmake scripts for nodejs, npm and yarn.

	* src/gsad_http_handler.c: Add new http handlers for gsa ng. The handlers will
	only be used if USE_GSA_NG is defined.

	* src/html/classic/ng/CMakeLists.txt: Add CMakeLists.txt for building and
	installing gsa ng.

	* src/html/classic/ng/src/web/css/images: Add symbolic link to the current css
	images. This is only required until gsa is completely based on gsa ng.

	* src/html/classic/ng/yarn.lock: Add a yarn lock file. This allows
	reproducable builds for gsa ng on different machines with different
	node environments.

