2016-12-12  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/html/classic/ng/package.json, src/html/classic/ng/src/utils.js: Remove
	dependency for x2js. There is no package for this x2js on npmjs.org. Therefore
	the npm version of debian stable seems to have issues with this package during
	installation. Instead use the already included version of x2js.

2016-12-12  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

