	file_content_response if extension is unkown.

2016-11-28  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.neto

	Allow to header for Cross-Origin Resource Sharing (CORS)

	src/gsad.c (main): Add new command line option for setting the
	"Access-Control-Allow-Origin" http header.

	src/gsad.c (add_cors_headers): Add new function to set
	Access-Control-Allow-Origin and Access-Control-Allow-Credential http headers
	in a response.

	src/gsad.c (send_response, send_redirect_to_uri, handle_request): Add cors
	header to responses.

