2016-10-05  Björn Ricks <bjoern.ricks@greenbone.net>

	* src/gsad_omp.c (save_task_omp, create_task_omp),
	* src/html/classic/omp.xsl (new_taks, html-edit-task-form): Use "0" as not set
	value instead of "--". Before it was mixed behavior by using "--" and "0" for
