	* src/html/classic/js/gsa_dashboard.js: Allow to set the title and it's count
	parameter via data attributes on the chart.

	* src/html/classic/graphics.xsl: Refactor charts to reuse more template code.
	All charts have been implemented twice. Using templates allows to use the same
	code for all chart generation. Also use new title attributes to set the chart
	titles directly. Additionally all charts and data source have now a common
	naming schema.

